miles away this whole time.

2253
01:38:53,750 --> 01:38:54,875
[KYON]
Hm?

2254
01:38:54,958 --> 01:38:56,916
Okay, but you really
don't need to apologize.

2255
01:38:57,000 --> 01:38:58,458
Don't tell me it's Haruhi again.

2256
01:38:58,541 --> 01:39:00,708
Is she causing more
weirdness to happen?

2257
01:39:00,791 --> 01:39:04,833
No... This doesn't have anything
to do with Miss Suzumiya.

2258
01:39:04,916 --> 01:39:07,208
But... It's just that...

2259
01:39:07,291 --> 01:39:08,708
I guess if I told you,

2260
01:39:08,791 --> 01:39:11,958
it wouldn't be such
a bad thing, after all.

2261
01:39:13,416 --> 01:39:13,916
[KYON]
Huh?

2262
01:39:14,000 --> 01:39:15,083
[thunder crash]

2263
01:39:15,166 --> 01:39:16,666
[KOIZUMI] At the beginning
of this episode,

2264
01:39:16,750 --> 01:39:20,083
the caption said ten heroines,
but we only saw eight of them!

2265
01:39:20,166 --> 01:39:22,583
Could I be one of the
two remaining heroines?!

2266
01:39:22,666 --> 01:39:24,250
[KYON]
You gotta be kidding me!

2267
01:39:24,333 --> 01:39:26,458
Is that what you've been
thinking about this whole time?!

2268
01:39:26,541 --> 01:39:27,666
Wait! I got it now!

2269
01:39:27,750 --> 01:39:29,625
The other heroine can only be...

2270
01:39:29,708 --> 01:39:31,166
...Mr. Arakawa!

2271
01:39:31,250 --> 01:39:35,166
I don't freaking care!

2272
01:39:36,375 --> 01:39:38,166
--It's ready!
--You made it?!

2273
01:39:38,250 --> 01:39:39,708
I want you to test it.

2274
01:39:39,791 --> 01:39:42,333
Okay, if you insist...

2275
01:39:43,333 --> 01:39:45,875
[KYON]
This is from the movie!

2276
01:39:49,083 --> 01:39:51,208
[KYON]
Hmm... The Asakura route, huh?

2277
01:39:51,291 --> 01:39:53,541
[NAGATO]
She is difficult to complete.

2278
01:39:53,625 --> 01:39:54,916
If you make one wrong choice,

2279
01:39:55,000 --> 01:39:57,458
you will arrive
at the bad ending.

2280
01:39:57,541 --> 01:39:58,791
[KYON]
This is too hard!

2281
01:39:58,875 --> 01:40:00,666
By the way, this
type of character is

2282
01:40:00,750 --> 01:40:03,291
more commonly known as yandare.

2283
01:40:03,375 --> 01:40:05,333
[KYON]
This is getting a little creepy.

2284
01:40:06,750 --> 01:40:09,875
[KYON] Okay...
I've seen this setup before.

2285
01:40:12,541 --> 01:40:15,708
Do you consider this type
of meeting scenario boring?

2286
01:40:15,791 --> 01:40:17,666
[KYON] That's an accident
not a meeting!

2287
01:40:17,750 --> 01:40:20,583
Wait, is this the Arakawa route?

2288
01:40:20,666 --> 01:40:22,791
Oh, you got Miss Mori
as a P.E. teacher.

2289
01:40:22,875 --> 01:40:24,208
[NAGATO]
Yes.

2290
01:40:24,291 --> 01:40:26,708
If you complete her stage,
she will become your maid.

2291
01:40:26,791 --> 01:40:29,875
[KYON] Okay... That's kinda
strange, but I can live with it.

2292
01:40:29,958 --> 01:40:32,750
And if you can make it to
the final stage and defeat her,

2293
01:40:32,833 --> 01:40:35,041
you will be rewarded
with a happy ending.

2294
01:40:35,125 --> 01:40:39,291
What in the name of all that's
holy is this game's genre?!

2295
01:40:39,375 --> 01:40:40,833
[NAGATO]
A love story?

2296
01:40:40,916 --> 01:40:44,041
