01:41:00,583 --> 01:41:05,500
[chomping]

2298
01:41:10,875 --> 01:41:12,500
Here we go!

2299
01:41:13,500 --> 01:41:15,583
[CHURUYA]
Nyon!

2300
01:41:15,666 --> 01:41:17,583
Nyon!

2301
