Nyoron...

2305
01:41:30,916 --> 01:41:33,750
Hey, Kyon! Hey, Kyon!

2306
01:41:33,833 --> 01:41:35,875
Do you have any smoked
cheese with you?

2307
01:41:35,958 --> 01:41:38,041
You already had some today.

2308
01:41:38,125 --> 01:41:40,250
[CHURUYA]
Nyoron...

2309
01:41:43,125 --> 01:41:43,583
[CHURUYA gasps]

2310
