[CHURUYA]
Hey, taxi!

2313
01:41:51,416 --> 01:41:53,250
[tires screech]

2314
01:42:02,041 --> 01:42:03,250
[click]

2315
01:42:04,250 --> 01:42:06,083
[CHURUYA]
Nyoron...

2316
01:42:06,791 --> 01:42:09,791
Hey, Mikuru! Mikuru!

2317
01:42:09,875 --> 01:42:13,416
I was wondering, do you know
how smoked cheese is made?

2318
01:42:13,500 --> 01:42:14,875
Google it.

2319
01:42:14,958 --> 01:42:16,666
[CHURUYA]
Nyoron...

2320
01:42:18,333 --> 01:42:21,166
Hey, Itsuki! Itsuki!

2321
01:42:21,250 --> 01:42:24,291
Smoked cheese is gonna be
the big thing this year, huh?

2322
01:42:24,375 --> 01:42:26,000
[KOIZUMI sighs]

2323
01:42:26,083 --> 01:42:29,208
[CHURUYA]
Nyoron...

2324
01:42:29,291 --> 01:42:31,541
Hey, Haru-nyan! Haru-nyan!

2325
01:42:31,625 --> 01:42:32,916
Let's do a "Smoked Cheese is

2326
01:42:33,000 --> 01:42:35,833
Obviously Awesome
