Hey, Nagatocchi! Nagatocchi!

2330
01:42:44,250 --> 01:42:46,791
Are there any books
about smoked cheese?

2331
01:42:46,875 --> 01:42:48,333
[NAGATO]
Who knows.

2332
01:42:48,416 --> 01:42:50,416
[CHURUYA]
Nyoron...

2333
01:43:16,208 --> 01:43:17,750
[KYON]
Here we go.

2334
01:43:17,833 --> 01:43:20,375
Rock, paper, scissors.
Loser takes out the trash.

2335
01:43:20,458 --> 01:43:23,541
One... two... three.

2336
01:43:23,625 --> 01:43:25,791
[CHURUYA]
Nyoron...

2337
01:43:26,166 --> 01:43:28,125
We're gonna have a fire drill.

2338
01:43:28,208 --> 01:43:30,375
Miss Churuya, you get
to put out the fire.

2339
01:43:30,458 --> 01:43:32,083
[CHURUYA]
Roger that!

2340
01:43:32,166 --> 01:43:33,291
Squirt, squirt, squirt.

2341
01:43:33,375 --> 01:43:34,416
