2342
01:43:34,500 --> 01:43:35,041
One.

2343
01:43:35,125 --> 01:43:35,583
Two.

2344
01:43:35,666 --> 01:43:36,083
Three.

2345
01:43:36,166 --> 01:43:36,708
Four.

2346
01:43:36,791 --> 01:43:37,416
Five.

