Where's Miss Churuya?

2348
01:43:38,375 --> 01:43:39,208
She didn't make it out in time.

2349
01:43:39,291 --> 01:43:40,833
Then she's dead.

2350
01:43:40,916 --> 01:43:42,625
[CHURUYA]
Nyoron...

2351
01:43:43,375 --> 01:43:45,375
Hey, Nagatocchi! Nagatocchi!

2352
01:43:45,458 --> 01:43:47,166
Will you play with me?

2353
