Ashakura.

2358
01:43:54,791 --> 01:43:55,708
Will

2359
01:43:55,791 --> 01:43:57,333
Impossible.

2360
01:43:57,416 --> 01:43:59,708
[CHURUYA]
Nyoron...

2361
01:44:01,708 --> 01:44:03,708
[keys click]

2362
01:44:08,166 --> 01:44:09,291
[KYON]
No.

2363
01:44:10,166 --> 01:44:11,875
[CHURUYA]
Nyoron...

