2372
01:44:38,166 --> 01:44:39,208
[
Ahh!

2373
01:44:39,291 --> 01:44:42,250
[grunts]

2374
01:44:42,333 --> 01:44:43,416
Hm?

2375
01:44:45,791 --> 01:44:47,750
[CHURUYA]
Huh?

2376
01:45:12,791 --> 01:45:14,625
Here we go.

2377
01:45:14,708 --> 01:45:17,041
We're goin' to town to look
for some mysterious things.

2378
01:45:17,125 --> 01:45:18,666
[CHURUYA giggles]

2379
01:45:18,750 --> 01:45:20,291
That looks pretty mysterious.

2380
01:45:20,375 --> 01:45:21,541
Okay, we're done.

2381
01:45:21,625 --> 01:45:23,625
[CHURUYA]
Nyoron...

2382
01:45:23,708 --> 01:45:25,875
We're gonna play baseball today!

2383
01:45:27,000 --> 01:45:29,125
You're out... as a player!

2384
01:45:29,208 --> 01:45:30,875
[CHURUYA]
Nyoron...

2385
01:45:30,958 --> 01:45:32,666
Let's hand out some flyers!

2386
01:45:35,000 --> 01:45:36,833
[CHURUYA]
Nyoron...

2387
01:45:36,916 --> 01:45:39,041
We're gonna go on
a trip tomorrow!

2388
01:45:39,125 --> 01:45:40,958
