2390
01:45:43,708 --> 01:45:45,250
[HARUHI]
Then we're not going.

2391
01:45:45,333 --> 01:45:47,041
[CHURUYA]
Nyoron...

2392
01:45:47,125 --> 01:45:49,666
Let's challenge the
Computer Club to a game!

2393
01:45:49,750 --> 01:45:50,625
Are you ready?

2394
01:45:50,708 --> 01:45:52,208
[CHURUYA]
Mm-hm!

2395
01:45:54,083 --> 01:45:55,958
[CHURUYA]
Nyoron...

2396
01:45:56,041 --> 01:45:57,500
