we'll give you a computer.

2406
01:46:18,041 --> 01:46:19,291
Challenge accepted.

2407
01:46:19,375 --> 01:46:21,875
And if you beat us,
we'll give you Miss Churuya.

2408
01:46:21,958 --> 01:46:23,500
